cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI

This paper primarily deals with the security issues related to IoT devices and proposes a solution using machine learning algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves network traffic classification and analysis, which falls under the category of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The use of machine learning algorithms for traffic classification suggests the possibility of the paper being categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper proposes a solution for large-scale networks, which could also fall under the category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
